    <h2>DCBL Suppression System — quiet-blower specialty</h2>
    <p>Zephyr's signature technology on Milano + Cypress + Anzio premium lines is the <b>DCBL Suppression System</b> — brushless DC motor + acoustic damping + impeller balance engineering that substantially reduces kitchen noise vs conventional AC-motor hoods. For service, DCBL motors are distinct replacement parts (higher cost + slightly longer lead) and include an electronic speed controller that can fail independently of the motor itself. Our techs verify motor generation via model number + serial before ordering parts — DCBL and conventional AC motors are not interchangeable even within the same visual product family.</p>
